// import React, { useState } from 'react';
import Button from 'react-bootstrap/Button';
import Form from 'react-bootstrap/Form';
import Modal from 'react-bootstrap/Modal';

function ModalRegister({show, handle}) {

  return (
    <>

      <Modal show={show} onHide={handle} centered size="md"  >
        <Modal.Title className='text-center fw-semibold pt-4 fs-1'>Register</Modal.Title>
        <Modal.Body className='modal-login'>
          <Form>
            <Form.Group className="mb-3" controlId="exampleForm.ControlInput1">
              <Form.Label>Full Name</Form.Label>
              <Form.Control
                type="text"
                placeholder="name@example.com"
                autoFocus
              />
            </Form.Group>
            <Form.Group className="mb-3" controlId="exampleForm.ControlInput1">
              <Form.Label>Email</Form.Label>
              <Form.Control
                type="email"
                autoFocus
              />
            </Form.Group>
            <Form.Group
              className="mb-3"
              controlId="exampleForm.ControlTextarea1"
            >
              <Form.Label>Password</Form.Label>
              <Form.Control
                type="password"
              />
            </Form.Group>
            <Form.Group className="mb-3" controlId="exampleForm.ControlInput1">
              <Form.Label>Number</Form.Label>
              <Form.Control
                type="number"
                autoFocus
              />
            </Form.Group>
          </Form>
          <Button className='btn-yellow w-100' onClick={handle}>
            Register
          </Button>
        </Modal.Body>
      </Modal>
    </>
  );
}

export default ModalRegister
